T02D1965:104b-0: @104b ` // sbyin sreg gi cho ga bzhugs /
T02D1965:104b-2: # // dpal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1965:104b-3: sbyin sreg gi rim pa ni /
T02D1965:104b-4: sa'i cho ga dang sta gon dang /
T02D1965:104b-5: thig rnams tshul bzhin byas la /
T02D1965:104b-6: thab khung yang lugs mthun par brus te /
T02D1965:104b-8: rnga mo dang bor bu'i sbangs dang //
T02D1965:104b-10: me tog nag po dri mi zhim pas byugs la /
T02D1965:104b-11: shin tu rtsub pa dang tsha ba dang dur khrod kyi thal bas kyang byugs la //
T02D1965:104b-12: yam shing yang de nyid las byung ba /
T02D1965:104b-13: rtse mo khrag dang dug dang yungs mar la sogs pa dang /
T02D1965:104b-14: drag po'i sreg rdzas ji ltar 'os pa bsag /
T02D1965:104b-15: bdag nyid kyi chas gos kyang dur ras dang g-yang
T02D1965:104b-16: gzhi dang gos nag la sogs pa bsham /
T02D1965:104b-17: de nas rdzas rnams g-yon du gzhag / mchod yon
T02D1965:104b-18: la sogs pa g-yas su gzhag / de nas bdag
T02D1965:104b-19: nyid stan med cing sra ba la rus sbal gyi
T02D1965:104b-23: khros pa'i sems kyis so bca' zhing rnal 'byor gnyis byas la //
T02D1965:104b-24: rjes su rnal 'byor la rang 'dra gzhug / rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor bya ba de la /
T02D1965:104b-25: rnal 'byor chen po rdzogs byas la //
T02D1965:104b-26: de nas thab yig aa las byung ba nag po 'od nag po 'phro ba /
T02D1965:104b-27: mthong ba tsam gyis kyang gsod par nus par bsam /
T02D1965:104b-28: yo byad kun kyang ya yis byin gyis brlabs la /
T02D1965:104b-29: rdzas re re 'ang 'od nag po 'phro ba /
T02D1965:104b-32: lha rnams la phul bas kyang khro ba dang gtum par 'gyur bar bsam /
T02D1965:104b-33: yi ge bcu bzhi pas thab dang rdzas kun bsangs la /
T02D1965:104b-34: thab tu brtsig / de nas me gnyer te /
T02D1965:104b-35: rigs ngan gyi khyim nas byung ba 'am /
T02D1965:104b-36: rdo drud pa las byung ba /
T02D1965:104b-37: yam shing la me sbar te /
T02D1965:104b-38: yi ge bcu bzhi pas bsangs la thab tu sbar
T02D1965:104b-39: de la yungs mar gang phul la rlung g-yab kyis
T02D1965:104b-41: dzv'a la ram dzv'a la ram /
T02D1965:104b-42: de nas mtshan ma brtag par bya //
T02D1965:105a-0: ltas bzang ba dang me lha bskyed de dang por mngon par byang chub pas rdo rje @105a * //
T02D1965:105a-1: sems dpa' bskyed de 'od du zhu ba'i gong bu las lha mo bzhi chad de /
T02D1965:105a-3: ram nag po de las byung ba'i rdo rje las /
T02D1965:105a-4: me lha 'khros [*khros?] pas zhes bya ba zhal la sogs pa gtso bo gnyis 'dra ba cig bsam /
T02D1965:105a-5: de nas ye shes kyi me lha ts'a rtsi k'as dgug ste /
T02D1965:105a-6: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
T02D1965:105a-7: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs 'byung po che //
T02D1965:105a-8: lha ya drang srong bram ze'i mchog / sreg blugs zhal zas bzhes slad du //
T02D1965:105a-9: 'bar ba'i nang du bzhugs su gsol //
T02D1965:105a-11: kro dha aagne che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat /
T02D1965:105a-12: de la zhabs bsil phul la /
T02D1965:105a-13: yi ge bcu bzhi pa'i gzhug la /
T02D1965:105a-14: aargham pra t'i tstsha che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat ces so //
T02D1965:105a-15: zhabs bsil yang sngags kyi mjug la /
T02D1965:105a-16: ni ri kham che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat /
T02D1965:105a-18: pra wa ra satk'a ra pra t'i tstsha che ge mo m'a ra ya h'um phat ces brjod do //
T02D1965:105a-19: de nas sgo ba gzhis dgug gzhug bya /
T02D1965:105a-20: de nas mig la sogs pa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
T02D1965:105a-21: lus ngag sems kyang byin gyis brlab //
T02D1965:105a-23: de nas zhabs bsil la sogs pa dang //
T02D1965:105a-25: rang gi sngags kyi mjug la bskul tshig dang bcas pas so //
T02D1965:105a-30: rdzas kun yi ge bcu bzhi pa'i mjug la bskul tshig dang bcas pas so //
T02D1965:105a-34: de nas me lha me 'bar ba'i rnam par 'gyur bar bsams la /
T02D1965:105a-35: yang thab dang rdzas bsangs la /
T02D1965:105a-36: 'bar ba'i nang du dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi tshul du ston to /
T02D1965:105a-37: de'i mig la sogs pa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
T02D1965:105a-38: lus la sogs pa byin gyis brlabs te /
T02D1965:105a-39: dbang bskul la ye shes 'khor lo dgug gzhug byas
T02D1965:105a-40: la dang po zhe sdang rdo rje la thun mong
T02D1965:105a-42: de nas sreg rdzas kun yi ge bcu bzhi pa'i sngags bskul tshig dang bcas pas 'bul te /
T02D1965:105a-45: de nas yang thab bsangs la /
T02D1965:105a-46: yang gti mug rdo rje dang /
T02D1965:105a-47: de de bzhin du rim pas dbul /
T02D1965:105a-48: tha mar ling+ga la bkug 'dren byas la /
T02D1965:105a-49: de nas gtub cing sreg / de nas ye shes pa gshegs su gsol /
T02D1965:105b-1: sreg rdzas lhag ma kun dbul te /
T02D1965:105b-3: ye shes kyi me lha gshegs /
T02D1965:105b-5: de nas bsngo ba dang smon lam bya /
